# Runbook

## Rotate Model Keys
1. Update `.env` with new API keys (e.g., Pinecone, Hugging Face).
2. Restart pods: `kubectl rollout restart deployment/lazy-ai -n lazy-ai`

## Purge User Data
Run: `python scripts/purge_user.py --user_id=123` (TODO: Implement script)

## Run No-Answer Tests
`cd model-pipeline && pytest tests/no_answer_suite/`

## Add Curriculum
1. Update `backend/config.py` with new standards.
2. Reindex vector DB: `python scripts/reindex.py` (TODO: Implement)
